title: Artem Malysh
text:
Artem Volodymyrovych Malysh (; born 15 July 2000) is a Ukrainian professional <a href="Association%20football">football</a> <a href="Goalkeeper%20%28association%20football%29">goalkeeper</a> who played for <a href="FC%20Inhulets%20Petrove">Inhulets Petrove</a>.
Career.
Early years.
Malysh is a product of <a href="FC%20Dynamo%20Kyiv">Dynamo Kyiv</a> sportive school system, after the short period in the local <a href="FC%20Kovel-Volyn%20Kovel">Kovel</a> youth school.
Inhulets Petrove.
In August 2020 he was transferred to the <a href="Ukrainian%20Premier%20League">Ukrainian Premier League</a> débutant <a href="FC%20Inhulets%20Petrove">Inhulets Petrove</a> and made his league debut on 21 February 2021, playing as a starting player in the home draw against <a href="FC%20Vorskla%20Poltava">Vorskla Poltava</a>.
